i wish i could just make up my mind sometimes.

i'm not really complaining, i'm more worrying than anything else.  i dotn know how to make decisions and keep them.  i could be thinking one thing one minute, and then the next my opinions will be totally different...and its not on the small things in my life either. its the decisions that effect my emotions.  the ones that  drive me mad.  

i just think to myself...darling, you'll be ok. 

maybe i'm kidding myself...maybe i'm not.  but i do know that i need to start to believe what i say or i'll never be ok.

i miss how things were a few months ago, at the the start of this year. i miss alot of things.  things seemed so peaceful then.  i was happier.  i didnt need as much as i do now.  i knew what i wanted.  i knew where i wanted to be.  and most of the time i was happy with what my situation was.  but now its so confusing and its not going the way i want it to.  it got all messed up.  

i supposed its all part of life.

i just want to play pretend for a little bit longer.

i dont really feel like going outside today.  but Hitler's School-O-Hair will drain me of all my money if i dont go... i didnt have my lazy sunday, and now i'm very tired because i didtn get to make up for it on monday either.  i need my day to just sit around and do nothing...its nice. 

i really need to start sleeping.

iggy and the stooges was amazing.  brian suprised me with vip tickets: tenth row.  it was sooooo awesome.  i'm all tired.  some cute little girl had her hand on my ass for about five minutes. (no complaining here)  as soon as we walked in, some old guy comes up to me and says "i think i'm in love"....my reaction: "i'm sorry"  then he tried to introduce me to someone...and apologized to brian...and i ran away.  i got hit on the whole way to my seat...it settled down after that thank god. i'm lucky i wore a bra...or it might have been worse...my shirt is cute, i just made it today, but its made weird, and, like now, when i dont wear a bra,  i'm pretty close to showing a little more than i wish to..but sence i'm at home by my self who  cares.

burn your bra's girls! 

haha just kidding...i do hate bras, but i cant burn mine i need them.

i watched brian fall asleep...sometimes its nice to do that because it makes me feel loved....i dont know why, but it does...no matter who i'm watching fall asleep.  but watching brian is my favorite..he's so damn cute.

iggy pop is today...i'm glad.

this weekend was fun.  i met a really beautiful girl.  she is super nice. super hot too. but she likes boys better. 

i sort of had a weird breakdown too...i felt so stupid.

oh yeah....and a trip to BFE...i dont want to explain it...because i dont want to remember it. 

my car is getting fixed right now.  yay.
and Jesus drives to Mexico to get her perscription filled.

blah...i went to cc last night.  it was pretty fun actually.  i danced...thats what i went to do isnt it?  i took jen, and she ended up totally hitting on this weird guy...and then we ended up driving this cute guy to his friends house because he got stranded...so me and jen ended up in lincoln park, and we sat there for a while. then we went home....i met her dogs...i was inside her house...no one goes inside her house!  lol...it was fun. and i ended up messing my thumb up pretty bad falling on my ass.  woo hoo.  as soon as i fell i had like three guys asking if i needed help up...but i just needed to sit there for a while...lol...i figured i went to the ground for a reason..i should stay for a minute.  

so not having power sucked.  not so much the not having power part..just the part where i was alone most of the black-out, staring at the walls because it was too dark to read, too dark to paint, too dark to do just about anything. i had alot of things to do when it was daylight...but i'm usually not up for much of the daylight hours.

i have iggy pop tickets....

5 of them to be exact

and i cant believe that i know exactly who i want to give the other four to.  Jen was with me last night when i got them, so i'm taking her, and i want Brian to go, he loves concerts...it usually doesnt even matter who is playing to him.  and shawna and billy really wanted to go, but i doubt they got tickets..the only bad thing is i only have room for one other person becides me jen and brian in his car, and neither shawna or billy can drive...i take that back..billy can he just doesnt have a working car.  grr.  i know they both really want to go, not just for iggy, but for sonic youth.  they are huge fans.  

jen and dan would be perfect together...lol...how weird.

i had fun last night.

i dont know what it is anymore, but i cant seem to make someone happy.  i honestly dont even know why i'm crying anymore.  i know its my fault...and i shoudltn be crying at all...but i cant seem to stop.  there is absolutely no reason for me to cry over anything.  mabye its because ithink i'm being used...or mabybe its because i know that i'm the only one in this with these feelings...i didnt care about that stuff before, but i seem to now.
